@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Add stable mood
POST {{baseUrl}}/mental/add-mood
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "happy",
  "stressLevel": 3,
  "sleepHours": 7.5,
  "notes": "Good routine today",
  "createdAt": "2026-05-04T10:00:00Z"
}

### Add high-stress mood
POST {{baseUrl}}/mental/add-mood
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "stressed",
  "stressLevel": 8,
  "sleepHours": 5.0,
  "notes": "Long work day",
  "createdAt": "2026-05-04T20:00:00Z"
}

### History
GET {{baseUrl}}/mental/history

### Analyze
POST {{baseUrl}}/mental/analyze
